menuconfig CONFIG_CMD
	bool "Configuration command channel (zbus)"
	depends on ZBUS
	help
	  Enables the config_cmd_chan zbus channel. Producers (e.g.
	  http_dashboard) publish config_cmd_event messages; consumers
	  (fake_sensors, sntp_sync) subscribe independently and act on
	  the commands. Producers never call consumers directly.
